== Prior license history ==

hipfire's canonical repository was originally MIT-licensed (LICENSE
added in commit b068a2ac, 2026-04-27). It briefly transitioned to
Apache 2.0 unilaterally in commit 79167568 (2026-05-19, on branch
relicense-apache2), then was course-corrected within the same branch
to the dual MIT/Apache-2.0 posture documented here. Existing
MIT-licensed copies in the wild remain governed by their MIT grant.
See docs/governance/relicense-2026-05.md for the full decision
record including the course-correction reasoning.

